{"word":"καταχέω","slug":"καταχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαταχέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, χέω</el> ‘pour’] <b>pour out/down (over),</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a></el> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> indicating the object anointed <b><a href='B:470 26:7'>Mt 26:7</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> simple <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:480 14:3'>Mk 14:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καταφωνέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καταχθείς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}